e wire tools wire the two rings hooked buckle, tighten one direction.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;&quot; class=&quot;img&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/static/index/img/tie-wire-2.jpg&quot; width=&quot;380&quot; height=&quot;285&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/static/index/img/tie-wire-3.jpg&quot; width=&quot;380&quot; height=&quot;285&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/static/index/img/tie-wire-5.jpg&quot; width=&quot;380&quot; height=&quot;285&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/static/index/img/tie-wire-4.jpg&quot; width=&quot;380&quot; height=&quot;285&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Loop Tie Wire', 'It is a metal wire used for tie sacks and sealing. Both ends of the wire into a ring-like process to facilitate the construction and improve efficiency.', '0', '1', '', '1529054391', '1529054391');
INSERT INTO `jz_archive` VALUES ('22', '12', '16', 'Spiral Growing Support', '0', '/uploads/20180615/259df1b4665e940f6e8e3874e39f7ce8.jpg', '', 'The products can be on your garden, for your tomato or all your plant to help growing good.', '&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;The products can be on your garden, for your tomato or all your plant to help growing good.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;The easiest way to support tomatoes or other vining plants is with these plant spirals. Instead of being tied to a wooden stake, the plant grows into the spiral, which gives natural support. This is the most popular way to support tomatoes in many countries and is easier than trying to tie plants to wooden stakes. Each steel spiral stake is about 6` long, but ships at only 3` long due to the reliable middle joint. Can be packaged as per your request and can also be powder coat painted to the color of your choice.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Plant spiral&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Ideal for growing tomatoes, cucumbers and other tall growing plants requiring support.&lt;br/&gt;Adjust the plant spiral to the correct length up to a maximum of 2 meters and attach using the fixings supplied.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Aluminum shelf&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;This shelf can be placed anywhere inside your greenhouse.&lt;br/&gt;At 150 x 15 cm, simply slot into the greenhouse frame to make the perfect windowsill.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;Other products have spiral plant supports, spiral ring plant supports, tomato spirals plant supports and so on.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;&quot; class=&quot;img&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/static/index/img/spiral-growing-support-1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/static/index/img/spiral-growing-support-2.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/static/index/img/spiral-growing-support-3.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/static/index/img/spiral-growing-support-4.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Spiral Growing Support', 'The products can be on your garden, for your tomato or all your plant to help growing good.', '0', '1', '', '1529054535', '1529054535');
INSERT INTO `jz_archive` VALUES ('23', '12', '17', 'Concrete Nails', '0', '/uploads/20180615/c77623de1a73260b4809ad6422bae876.jpg', '', 'It is absolutely impossible to imagine the repair without concrete nails in this work, and especially when it comes to construction work.', '&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;It is absolutely impossible to imagine the repair without concrete nails in this work, and especially when it comes to construction work. Concrete nails - one of the most common types of nails used by both professionals and amateurs. Concrete nails are widely used to connect the wooden elements and structures, as well as fixing them soft materials. The structure of the nail has a circular section and a flat or conical head. Roughness before the cap significantly improves the reliability of the connection.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;All this type nails are divided into the following types: electro-galvanized, hot-dip galvanized nails, as well as acid-resistant, stainless steel and copper nails.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;If the nail should be left inside the structure, it is best to use nails from hot galvanized steel. Black nails intended for temporary attachment rust appears on them even after contact with air. For the interior, you can use electro-galvanized nails or black nails. acid-resistant required for particularly difficult places. Copper nails have a decorative hat used in the decoration.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;&quot; class=&quot; list-paddingleft-2&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;It is harder with excellent fixing strength.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Excellent anti-bending, anti-crack and safety.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;With various special nail heads(headless, round flat head or square head) and shank types(smooth shank, ring shank, twisted shank, twilled shank).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;It is used in construction and other industry fields.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;&quot; class=&quot;img&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/static/index/img/concrete-steel-nail-1.jpg&quot; width=&quot;380&quot; height=&quot;285&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/static/index/img/concrete-steel-nail-2.jpg&quot; width=&quot;380&quot; height=&quot;285&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/static/index/img/concrete-steel-nail-3.jpg&quot; width=&quot;380&quot; height=&quot;285&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/static/index/img/concrete-steel-nail-4.jpg&quot; width=&quot;380&quot; height=&quot;285&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Concrete Nails', 'It is absolutely impossible to imagine the repair without concrete nails in this work, and especially when it comes to construction work.', '0', '1', '', '1529054608', '1529054608');
